No. 610. Edwin S. Hartwell Lumber Company, Petitioner, v. The United States; and John Spry Lumber Company, Petitioner, v. The United States. No. 611. March 19, 1906. Mr. Jacob Newman, Mr. Salmon 0. Levinson and Mr. Benjamin V. Becker for petitioners. The Attorney General and The Solicitor General for respondent.

Petitions for writs of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
